name: Bích Phương
description: '''Bùi Thị Bích Phương''' (born 30 September 1989), better known as '''Bích Phương''' is a Vietnamese singer. She entered the entertainment industry as a contestant of Season 3 of ''[[Vietnam Idol (season 3)|Vietnam Idol]]'' in 2010, and has since been established as one of Vietnam's most popular singers of the 2010s.
